-- New Mauritius Hotels Says Its Full-Year Profit Declined 44% to $22 Million
-- B y   K a m l e s h   B h u c k o r y
-- 2010-12-21T12:54:59Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-21/new-mauritius-hotels-says-its-full-year-profit-declined-44-to-22-million.html
New Mauritius Hotels Ltd. said full-
year profit declined 44 percent compared with a year earlier.  Net income retreated to 659.78 million rupees in the year
through September from 1.18 billion rupees in 2009, it said in a
statement on the website of the Port Louis-based Stock Exchange
of Mauritius today.  Revenue fell to 6.83 billion rupees from 7.4 billion
rupees, it said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Ana Monteiro at 
 amonteiro4@bloomberg.net  